comments:
At first it almost seem completely scrambled, but after the first 10 or so I started noticing a pattern: first how the shapes were denominated, then the colors. Around halfway was when I had a firm grip on the rules and was able to just continue practicing and hammering down the meanings. All done without notes.

The hardest part was probably choosing my partner's prompt; was it supposed to be a 50/50 between the two colors? Or was there a pattern/assigned color that I just missed?
